{
  "stem": "7302.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there's two others.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There's--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then is Jordan, and then is Jonathan.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was just in April we was having Jonathan's bar mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So the three-- his three sons already went through bar mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My husband, when we came to Toronto, we lived with my sister a couple of months.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was saying, we have to find a place for ourselves.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we rented a flat.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We lived there-- I don't know how long-- not too long, because they didn't let the kids to bring in any other kids-- you know-- friends or any.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I told my sister.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she was saying, you know what?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Come and live with us again for a while.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then when you will be able to find another place where you can be free, you'll go.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we went back to her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We lived with her another-- maybe a 1/2 a year.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we found another flat, which one was OK.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We lived there till-- till we got a house.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We lived there quite a few years-- maybe 10 years.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't remember exactly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Have you worked here?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the first couple of months or a year, or-- I didn't work.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I have been at home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My sister used to work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Everyone went to work, and I have been in the house preparing supper, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My husband got his job right away, so he worked.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "After that-- so I went in the evenings-- I went to learn a bit English.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "When I just got the basics a little bit.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because we came to Canada, I didn't know not one word of English.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a chance, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My watch stopped.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my sister told me, you know what?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You go over to Simpsons.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
